PLAYER_OF_THE_MONTH.notes: Southampton kept three clean sheets in four matches thanks to the handy work of Fraser Forster.

GOAL_OF_THE_MONTH.notes: Maddison scored with a stunning curler from distance in Leicester's 5-2 win at Man City.
Son's individual run and finish in Spurs' London derby with Chelsea provided the South Korean with his third PL award.
A second Goal of the Month award for the South Korean after a solo run from his own half was finished against Burnley on 7 December 2019.

PLAYER_OF_THE_MONTH.notes: Four goals and one assist helped Tottenham Hotspur's Son Heung-min become the first Asian player to win the award.
Son netted five times and provided one assist in Tottenham Hotspur's six wins in April.
Son sparkled in October, registering four goals and two assists to help his Spurs side finish the month in third place.

GOAL_OF_THE_SEASON.notes: The Spurs attacker's solo run and finish against Burnley came in December at the Tottenham Hotspur Stadium.
